# lapce v0.4.6 | rust workspace (hardening fork)
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
▸ Run:      cargo run --bin lapce
▸ Build:    cargo build --workspace
▸ Test:     cargo test --workspace
▸ Fmt:      cargo fmt --all --check
▸ Lint:     cargo clippy --profile ci
▸ Release:  cargo build --profile release-lto
▸ macOS:    make app   (or: make binary / make dmg)
▸ MSRV:     1.87.0 · edition 2024 · Apache-2.0
